					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287" rend="visible">
						<summary>The revised recension of Maimonides' Sefer mitsṿot in the Hebrew translation of <name type="person" role="translator">Mosheh ibn Tibon</name>. </summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he">Hebrew</textLang>
						<msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287">
							<locus from="1r" to="140v"/>
							<title xml:lang="en">Sefer ha-mitsṿot </title>
							<title xml:lang="he">ספר המצות </title>
							<note>
								<p>Folios 3-11 contain an index of the mitsṿot in their numerical order. A note on the margin of folio 11r states that the last 80 entries have been omitted by the scribe, because they were missing in the codex from which he copied. </p>
								<p>Folio 128-129 contain an index of the mitsṿot in the order in which they occure in the parashayot of the Pentateuch. </p>
							</note>
							<author key="http://viaf.org/viaf/100185495">
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/100185495" xml:lang="en">Maimonides, Moses, 1135-1204 </persName>
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/100185495" xml:lang="he">משה בן מימון, 1138-1204 </persName>
							</author>
							<colophon xml:lang="he">תם ונשלם. התהלה ושבח לבורא עולם. על ידי<name type="person" role="scribe"> יחיאל ח"י הסופר בכ"ר יואב כת"ב ע"ה מביתאל</name> פה ב<name type="place">ריאיטי</name> שנת <date when="1421" calendar="Hebrew">קפ"א</date> לפרט ג' בסיון במצות הנכבד כמה"ר משה הרופא יר"א בכמ"ר יצחק זצ"ל. ברוך נותן ליעף כח.<locus n="139v"/>
							</colophon>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Parchment codex of the 15th century.</p>
