									<p>140 folios (+ 3 modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end).  </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>14 quires of 10 leaves each. </p>
									<p>Catchwords at the end of the quires, partly cut away. </p>
								</collation>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1 " ruledLines="25" writtenLines="25">
									<p>Uniform layout. Visible pricking and ruling with a hard-point object.  </p>
									<p>Last line written outside the ruling.  </p>
									<p>Marginal notes, occasionally mutilated in the trimming.  </p>
									<p>Sections enumerated with Hebrew letters in larger characters.  </p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
