						<additions>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="owner">Eli'ezer bar Yehudah ha-Rofe of L'Aquila</name>: inscribed (folio 1r). </p>
							<p>A contract of sale, folio 140r, of the present manuscript by Refa'el ben Yitsḥaḳ ha-Rofe of <name type="place">Rieto </name>to the heirs of Mosheh ha-Rofe of <name type="place">L'Aquila</name>. </p>
							<p>Several censor's erasures, by <name type="person" role="censor">Andrea del Monte</name> (active in the second half of the 16th century), inscribed (folio 139v). </p>
						</additions>
